---
const coreScenes = [
  '技术调研：对比 Vite vs Turbopack',
  '生态分析：Rust GUI 框架现状',
  '架构研究：NotebookLM 技术栈',
  '深度新知：AI Agent 最新进展',
];

const triggerSignals = [
  '“deep search ...”',
  '“详细搜索 ... / 帮我查一下 ...”',
  '“深入研究一下 ...”',
  'Brave 结果太浅 → 自动升级',
];
---

<section class="search-decision-tree" aria-label="OpenClaw 搜索工具决策树">
  <header class="tree-header">
    <h2>OpenClaw 搜索工具决策树 — 使用场景指南</h2>
    <p>Brave Search · web_fetch · Codex CLI Deep Search · 何时用哪个？</p>
  </header>

  <div class="tree-canvas" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg class="tree-lines" viewBox="0 0 1120 920" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <defs>
        <marker id="arrow-blue" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="7" refY="4" orient="auto">
          <path d="M0,0 L8,4 L0,8 Z" fill="#60a5fa" />
        </marker>
        <marker id="arrow-green" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="7" refY="4" orient="auto">
          <path d="M0,0 L8,4 L0,8 Z" fill="#34d399" />
        </marker>
        <marker id="arrow-red" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="7" refY="4" orient="auto">
          <path d="M0,0 L8,4 L0,8 Z" fill="#fb7185" />
        </marker>
        <marker id="arrow-orange" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="7" refY="4" orient="auto">
          <path d="M0,0 L8,4 L0,8 Z" fill="#f59e0b" />
        </marker>
        <marker id="arrow-purple" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="7" refY="4" orient="auto">
          <path d="M0,0 L8,4 L0,8 Z" fill="#a78bfa" />
        </marker>
      </defs>
      <path class="line-blue" d="M560 86 V142" marker-end="url(#arrow-blue)" />
      <path class="line-green" d="M638 184 C760 184 790 142 870 142" marker-end="url(#arrow-green)" />
      <path class="line-red" d="M560 230 V292" marker-end="url(#arrow-red)" />
      <path class="line-green" d="M638 334 C760 334 792 326 870 326" marker-end="url(#arrow-green)" />
      <path class="line-red" d="M560 380 V446" marker-end="url(#arrow-red)" />
      <path class="line-red" d="M446 504 C350 504 310 512 245 536" marker-end="url(#arrow-red)" />
      <path class="line-green" d="M560 548 V606" marker-end="url(#arrow-green)" />
      <path class="line-purple dashed" d="M430 664 C380 664 365 666 322 676" marker-end="url(#arrow-purple)" />
      <path class="line-purple dashed" d="M690 664 C742 664 760 666 802 676" marker-end="url(#arrow-purple)" />
      <path class="line-purple" d="M560 736 V782" marker-end="url(#arrow-purple)" />
      <path class="line-blue" d="M560 832 C486 832 444 840 386 864" marker-end="url(#arrow-blue)" />
      <path class="line-orange" d="M560 832 C634 832 676 840 734 864" marker-end="url(#arrow-orange)" />
    </svg>

    <span class="line-label label-url-yes">是</span>
    <span class="line-label label-url-no">否</span>
    <span class="line-label label-simple-yes">是</span>
    <span class="line-label label-simple-no">否</span>
    <span class="line-label label-deep-yes">是</span>
    <span class="line-label label-deep-no">否</span>

    <article class="tree-node start-node">
      <span class="node-icon">👤</span>
      <strong>用户提出搜索需求</strong>
      <p>“帮我查 ... / 搜一下 ...”</p>
    </article>

    <article class="tree-node decision-node url-node">
      <strong>有明确 URL?</strong>
      <p>用户给了链接 / 网址</p>
    </article>

    <article class="tool-card fetch-card">
      <span class="tool-icon">🔗</span>
      <h3>web_fetch</h3>
      <p>直接获取页面，markdown</p>
      <strong>秒级、精准获取页面内容</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="detail-card fetch-detail-card">
      <strong>📄 智能读取“下载全文”</strong>
      <p>▶ 总结这个 GitHub README</p>
      <span>场景：单页、精准信息拉取</span>
    </article>

    <article class="tree-node decision-node simple-node">
      <strong>简单事实查询?</strong>
      <p>一条结果即可回答<br />需要快速响应</p>
    </article>

    <article class="tool-card brave-card">
      <span class="tool-icon">🌐</span>
      <h3>Brave Search</h3>
      <p>web_search API · 搜索优化片段</p>
      <strong>&lt;2s · 轻量 · 高并发</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="detail-card brave-detail-card">
      <ul>
        <li>今天美元兑人民币汇率</li>
        <li>Python 3.14 发布日期</li>
        <li>Next.js 最新版本</li>
      </ul>
      <span>场景：快速事实、时效信息、简单查询</span>
    </article>

    <article class="tree-node decision-node deep-node">
      <strong>复杂 / 多源 / 深度研究?</strong>
      <p>需要交叉验证 · 多个来源<br />deep search · 详细报告</p>
    </article>

    <article class="default-card">
      <strong>😎 Brave（默认）</strong>
      <p>不确定时先用 Brave</p>
    </article>

    <article class="codex-card">
      <span class="tool-icon">🤖</span>
      <h3>Codex CLI Deep Search</h3>
      <p>codex exec · gpt-5.3-codex · 多轮搜索 · 报告输出</p>
      <strong>1–2min · 综合调度 · Telegram 回执</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="side-card core-card">
      <h3>🎯 核心场景</h3>
      <ul>
        {coreScenes.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
      </ul>
      <span>场景：需要深度、多源分析的任务</span>
    </article>

    <article class="side-card signal-card">
      <h3>⚡ 触发信号</h3>
      <ul>
        {triggerSignals.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
      </ul>
      <span>场景：用户显式表达深度需求</span>
    </article>

    <article class="mode-choice-card">
      <strong>执行模式选择</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="mode-card sync-card">
      <h3>⚡ 同步模式</h3>
      <p>短查询 · &lt;1min · 直接返回</p>
      <span>可通过命令控制 Brave 兜底</span>
    </article>

    <article class="mode-card async-card">
      <h3>🕒 自动调度模式</h3>
      <p>长研究 · 1–2min · 结果通知</p>
      <span>耗时任务 / 深度分析任务 → 异步更可靠</span>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="mobile-flow">
    <article>
      <span>STEP 1</span>
      <h3>有明确 URL?</h3>
      <p>有链接就直接用 <strong>web_fetch</strong>，优先精准读取单页内容。</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <span>STEP 2</span>
      <h3>只是简单事实查询?</h3>
      <p>一条结果能回答、需要快速响应时，用 <strong>Brave Search</strong>。</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <span>STEP 3</span>
      <h3>需要复杂 / 多源 / 深度研究?</h3>
      <p>需要交叉验证、多个来源、详细报告时，用 <strong>Codex CLI Deep Search</strong>。</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <span>DEFAULT</span>
      <h3>不确定时先用 Brave</h3>
      <p>如果 Brave 结果太浅，再升级到 Deep Search。</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
